injectReward.t.sol
├── when contract is killed
│   └── it should revert with ContractKilled
├── when contract is paused
│   └── it should revert with Paused
├── when caller does not have REWARD_MANAGER_ROLE
│   └── it should revert with AccessControlUnauthorizedAccount
└── when caller has REWARD_MANAGER_ROLE and contract is live
    ├── when amount is greater than zero
    │   ├── when timestamp is in the past
    │   │   ├── when timestamp is before startWeekCursor
    │   │   │   └── it should revert with InvalidTimestamp
    │   │   └── when timestamp is after startWeekCursor
    │   │       ├── it should transfer tokens from caller to contract
    │   │       ├── it should increase lastTokenBalance
    │   │       ├── it should increase totalDistributed
    │   │       └── it should increase tokensPerWeek for the corresponding week
    │   ├── when timestamp is in the future
    │   │   ├── it should transfer tokens from caller to contract
    │   │   ├── it should increase lastTokenBalance
    │   │   ├── it should increase totalDistributed
    │   │   └── it should increase tokensPerWeek for the corresponding week
    │   └── when timestamp is current
    │       ├── it should transfer tokens from caller to contract
    │       ├── it should increase lastTokenBalance
    │       ├── it should increase totalDistributed
    │       └── it should increase tokensPerWeek for the current week
    └── when caller doesn't have enough tokens
        └── it should revert
